                            <p>LEARNING LAB</p>
                            <p>The first day amplifies the connection between Russian- and German-based artists and technologists pushing both virtual and physically embodied performance, with digital and movement tracks. This free open learning space is a chance for audiences in Russia and online to discover new skills and interact with leading practitioners from the program.</p>
                            <p>This includes Berlin-native startup cables.gl, a powerful 3D environment that runs inside browsers (with free beta), discussions of AI, live and generative visuals, music synthesis with free and open source software, and butoh as a link between Berlin techno and performers across Russia and eastern Asia.</p>
                            <p>Open to online audiences with opportunities to discuss and ask questions.</p>
