                            CDM has been a leading influential outlet for cutting-edge creative technology in music and audiovisual media since 2005, read by a quarter-million readers monthly, and a platform for community in music technology. In 2020-2021, CDM will partner with the Guthman Competition of Georgia Tech University to co-host the world’s top prize in musical instrument design, along with partnerships with MUTEK Forum [CA], GAMMA_PRO [RU], ARTYPICAL [RU], and ongoing partnerships with CTM Festival [DE].
                            <a target="_blank" href="https://cdm.link">https://cdm.link</a></p>
